//Task 1: Blow me away - says the paper airplane!
Step 1. Fold paper in half lengthwise (specify which side of paper is being folded)
Step 2. On one half take a corner opposite of the folded side  and fold the corner on the crease.
Step 3. Take the top of the newly formed triangle and fold it to form another triangle with one side along the crease.
Step 4. Repeat last step.
Step 5. Flip over to other side.
Step 6. Use steps 2 through 4 using the same side of the paper as you did on the other side.
